E-commerce API
This API provides user management, product management, order management, and cart management functionalities for an e-commerce platform.
Features



Getting Started

Prerequisites
Python 3.8 or higher
Django 3.2 or higher
Django REST Framework 3.13 or higher
Installing
Clone the repository:



Install the required packages:
pip install -r requirements.txt


Make migrations and apply them:
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate


Create a superuser:
python manage.py createsuperuser


Run the development server:
python manage.py runserver

Authorization: Bearer [Token]

Now you can access the API at http://127.0.0.1:8000/
